<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.10.5">
<l>tiṟamuṭai valattā ṟīviṉai perukkā</l>
<l>taṟamuya lāḻip paṭaiyavaṉ kōyiṉ</l>
<l>maṟuvil vaṇcuṉaicūḻ māliruñ cōlai</l>
<l>puṟamalai cārap pōvatu kiṟiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without increasing the fiery karma with firm  strength</l>
<l>the way  is going to approach the outer mountain</l>
<l>of Māliruñcōlai surrounded by flawless generous mountain pools,</l>
<l>the temple of him with the discus weapon who strives for justice.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
